FT  23 APR 93 / World News in Brief: Waco investigation starts
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Work started on removing bodies from the remains of the cult compound at
Waco, Texas, in which 86 are believed to have died. Investigators are
looking into the possibility that David Koresh's followers died in a mass
murder rather than suicide.
