<HEADLINE>
FT  23 APR 93 / FT Quarterly Review of Personal Finance (34): The
top-performing collective funds over five years
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Tables show the value, as at April 1, of a Pound 1,000 investment over
different periods. Unittrusts are given on an offer-to-bid basis withnet
income reinvested. Investment trusts areon a mid-market basis with net
incomereinvested. The order in which trusts arelisted is based on
performance over fiveyears, so that funds with less than five
years'performance are omitted. All of the figures on this page are provided
by Finstat, the Financial Times Statistics Service.
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
UNIT TRUSTS
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
UK General
